freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Today is 4th day post-vaccine #2.  28 h after vaccine #2 (6 pm Tu 2/16) I felt achy and ran a temp of 103 deg F until I took a Tylenol PM.  Fever and aches were gone when I woke up 2/17. My arm where I got the 2nd vaccine was sore on the 16th, but not excessively so.
